description: Publishing, snapshots, and ISR behavior
alwaysApply: true
---
- Publishing flips `status` to `published`, writes a full JSON snapshot to `trip_versions`, then revalidates affected routes only (homepage and the specific trip page).
- Use Next.js ISR revalidation on Netlify; do not trigger full site rebuilds.
- Provide a visible success/failure toast in admin.
